{"tid":1824287,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"張丹峰含X望實洪欣   一家三口結伴回港過年","createTime":"2020-01-14T10:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T11:44:00.000Z","uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"381ea368eff2a145ab76808392a52dd2564916b3","tid":1824287,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T10:22:07.000Z","msg":"洪欣和大陸男星張丹峰結婚多年，去年傳出張丹峰背妻出軌，搭上經理人畢瀅，婚姻出現暗湧。可幸張丹峰箍煲成功，豪擲150萬元買下一部名貴跑車冧老婆。又經常留港陪太太，早前就被本報讀者透過《爆相爆片》分享兩公婆在銅鑼灣拍拖買糖。<br />\n<br />\n日前又有大陸網民在機場發現張丹峰一家三口的縱影，當時洪欣身穿長褸戴着耳機，而張丹峰雖然戴着太陽眼鏡，但全程望住太太，含情脈脈。當差不多登機時，張丹峰走向大仔張鎬濂交代了幾句，兩父子有講有笑全無隔膜。相信今趟一家三口準備返港過年。<br />\n<br />\n近期兩夫婦經常出雙入對，先是5月洪欣夫婦帶同女兒，到哈爾濱出席婚宴，當時二人表現親暱，已打破離婚傳聞。雖然張鎬濂非張丹峰親子，不過張丹峰一向視如己出，就算他同洪欣2014年誕下西囡囡張晞彤，亦沒有減少對鎬濂的愛護。"},{"pid":"868f304b7320a03c43848d3385b3a661094aeac8","tid":1824287,"uid":48905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T10:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LEeHiB5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLEeHiB5.jpg&h=52914a2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abca0735e4762081ca8eeba96eb745de1bd0a002","tid":1824287,"uid":48905,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T10:22:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zEMOeav.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzEMOeav.png&h=4d4c6e53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"076a96fa613f2e3ca73406c155310fcb8ada7d8a","tid":1824287,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T10:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uiEPH4n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuiEPH4n.jpg&h=59bbc081&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"723475c4142f43ee3d604f0e31f0df15783c4e36","tid":1824287,"uid":154907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T10:33:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7qrB7yX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7qrB7yX.jpg&h=